Trade/Device Name(s): TaiDoc Pro I Glucose Test Strip
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for TaiDoc Pro I Glucose Test Strip for quantitative measurement of glucose in whole blood using compatible meters.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from finger and alternative sites, for use with compatible blood glucose meters and monitors by professionals and people with diabetes mellitus at home to aid monitoring of diabetes control; not for diagnosis/screening of diabetes or use on neonates.
